\SE[16]Oh, delicious...! \SE[15]This might be the first time
I've ever felt something so delicious up until now...!

\SE[56]I haven't been eating normal meals for a long time...
\SE[55]Vita also put in a lot of effort...

\SE[36]If it's this delicious, I'll end up gaining
weight...! \SE[55]Vita... She's really stepped up her
game...!!

\SE[16]W-Well...? \!\SE[42]I can handle something like this
with ease...?

\SE[13]Ah, after meals... there's a new trending dessert,
you know...! \SE[13]It's called chocolate... it's coming
soon...!

\SE[2]Chocolate...? \SE[36]Even though I've never heard of
it before, it sounds so sweet and enchanting that it might
melt my heart...

\SE[72]While you were sleeping, these snacks were imported
from Cordain. \!\SE[79]It seems like they're so popular that
there are long queues forming.

\SE[2]Huh...? So you went through the trouble of lining up
to buy them...?

\SE[21]I-It's not a big deal...! \!\SE[10]Compared to
thinking about Lady Lunaroa, this is nothing...!
\SE[90](She's saying the same thing as earlier...)

\SE[4]Hey, Tita? \SE[3]Is it okay if I sit in the seat next
to Lunaroa? It's empty there, right?

\SE[4]Tita has worked really hard too... I think she has the
right to \SE[3]... well, I can't really say since I'm not in
a position to.

\SE[11]If I were to be honest... \!\SE[18]I do have some
mixed feelings...

\SE[95]Because Tita was there... I was able to fight with
peace of mind all this time... \SE[18]If it wasn't for her,
I don't think I would have been able to save Luna.

\SE[59]That's why... \!\SE[54]I think it's wrong that Tita's
efforts aren't being rewarded... I also... feel like I'm
mistaken...
\SE[4]W-Wait, me...!? \!\SE[12]I see, it was about me...

\SE[2]If Tita-chan is okay with it... \.Shall we eat
together over here...? \!\SE[0]I'm sure the food will taste
even better that way.

\SE[12]Someone like me... having a meal next to Lady
Lunaroa...!? \!\SE[14]N-No, that's not possible...! If I get
involved, Lady Lunaroa will be tainted! \!\SE[23]I will
become a stain if I'm involved...!!

\SE[58]... Yeah, we reached an agreement. \!\SE[47] Sigh, I
guess there's no helping it...

\SE[9]I-I really ended up next to...! \!\SE[28]Lady
Lunaroa...\.right next to her...!!

\SE[47] (Beside me is my beloved Laura...\.The Alice girls
rely on me as their Mama... \!\SE[45] When I wake up, Tita
adores me...)

\SE[36] (So there really is such a thing as a popular
phase...)

\SE[4]Excuse me for interrupting your conversation!
\!\SE[12]Something big is happening outside!
